Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.00,0:02:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.58,0:02:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個通過與同契者同契成為強大的力量的種族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.17,0:02:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其中被稱為最強種族的七煌寶樹之一 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.53,0:02:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及和她締結契約的人類少年 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.04,0:02:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩個人朝著傳說之地煌珠樂園踏上了旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.32,0:02:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第七唱 並唱頌之決意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.50,0:02:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷德·望·朱魯愛特是哪個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.97,0:03:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種人誰會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.47,0:03:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這...這傢伙是怪物嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.28,0:03:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃...快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.07,0:03:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼啊 這些傢伙 太弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.67,0:03:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 葛雷亞茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.48,0:03:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許不是在這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.93,0:03:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪 據情報說是空賊的啊 可可威特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.42,0:03:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.54,0:03:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說 你知道七煌寶樹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.05,0:03:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七...七煌寶樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.44,0:03:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 什麼啊 不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就沒你什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.82,0:03:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.15,0:03:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吃 龍威的手藝真是不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.68,0:04:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入口綿甜醇厚和順而又不是太濃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.70,0:04:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實在是絕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.24,0:04:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果再有好的材料的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.24,0:04:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一日三十種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.46,0:04:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獲取所有必需的能量和營養
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.90,0:04:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能填飽肚子就什麼都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.91,0:04:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是沒變 完美主義啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.07,0:04:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太完美的男人會被女人討厭的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.82,0:04:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷是不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.48,0:04:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨得恰到好處不用擔心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.42,0:04:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.01,0:04:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.41,0:04:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩個人都...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.86,0:04:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 確認一下明天的行程吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.09,0:04:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我們生活的世界Guardian的地圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.20,0:04:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後這條線就是至今為止所走的路程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.14,0:04:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠樂園往這個方向走行嗎 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.33,0:04:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.24,0:04:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.58,0:04:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊的地域還沒有製出正確的地圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.16,0:04:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好遠啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.73,0:05:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還只走了這麼一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.18,0:05:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.83,0:05:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照現在的速度走完這個大陸都不知道要什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼點路如果能飛的話就是一眨眼的功夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.42,0:05:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是有空賊艇的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.60,0:05:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.85,0:05:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空賊艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.03,0:05:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好 要墜落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏面有戰鬥過的跡象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.08,0:05:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小型艇不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機組人員似乎都已離機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.95,0:05:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀 好慘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.87,0:05:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平安著陸的衝擊下掉落的零件把裏面搞得亂七八糟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.59,0:05:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在幹什麼 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.03,0:05:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有者不是丟下這個逃了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.83,0:05:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在想我們收下要不要緊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.44,0:06:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說想把這修好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.21,0:06:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前經常被老大叫去修理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.39,0:06:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種程度的話馬上就可以搞定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.55,0:06:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾 我會駕駛這個帶你去煌珠樂園的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.94,0:06:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 就是說沒找到七煌寶樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.81,0:06:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.94,0:06:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼下正繼續搜尋中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.21,0:06:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到那傢伙也這麼沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.53,0:06:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.64,0:06:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒睡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.45,0:06:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 想盡量早點修好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.70,0:06:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.10,0:06:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去煌珠樂園的話這個樣子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.13,0:06:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也是原因之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.54,0:06:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想在天上飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.66,0:06:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟過慣了空盜的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.41,0:07:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.54,0:07:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.31,0:07:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 這個已經沒後備的了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.52,0:07:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.47,0:07:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍威真是什麼都行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.63,0:07:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,菜不是燒得很好吃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.15,0:07:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛船的修理也在行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.31,0:07:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.29,0:07:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥也那麼強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.37,0:07:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十全十美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.66,0:07:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完美 太高抬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是有缺點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.95,0:07:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍威也有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.19,0:07:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 怎麼也改不了的壞習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.10,0:07:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼 庫魯斯補佐官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.51,0:07:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得了滿分但為什麼留我一個人補習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.03,0:08:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後你就會明白的 龍威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.13,0:08:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來告訴你你的缺點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.72,0:08:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 狀況不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.04,0:08:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.62,0:08:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣能飛了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.20,0:08:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 主引擎我已經完完全全修好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.59,0:08:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以這艘艇的最大航程來說Guardian的邊際都沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠樂園呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.21,0:08:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是一次性到達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.28,0:08:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.27,0:08:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.60,0:08:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 那個 那麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早就知道會是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.05,0:08:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才是測試 測試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.08,0:08:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在開始正式進行修理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.41,0:09:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 龍威去哪兒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說是和奇雅去買東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.45,0:09:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 龍 這個這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.42,0:09:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,買下這個乾貨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.33,0:09:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔 這個多少錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩又會抱怨的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.26,0:09:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又沒關係 反正很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.75,0:09:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不吃個飽的話緊急關頭不就同契不了了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.41,0:09:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 是 看中的都買吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔 這個我買兩個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.95,0:09:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.46,0:09:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要買那麼多嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.66,0:09:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到他們了哦 葛雷亞茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次不會錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.28,0:09:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行動嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.76,0:10:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次不會爆炸了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.65,0:10:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事的 前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.76,0:10:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仔細檢查過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.43,0:10:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 這由誰來駕駛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那當然是我嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.70,0:10:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼 放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.91,0:10:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別開玩笑了 我還不想年紀輕輕地就這麼死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的在飛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.91,0:10:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全修好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是這麼說了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.17,0:11:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了 龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直陪著酷 沒睡過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.44,0:11:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事 我也還算年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.70,0:11:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.08,0:11:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫得太投入的話分別的時候會不捨得哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.74,0:11:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.50,0:11:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過那也到時候再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於要上場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.90,0:11:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備好了嗎 可可威特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.71,0:11:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.90,0:11:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論去哪兒都陪著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.85,0:11:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK 那出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.47,0:11:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.24,0:11:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葛雷亞茲 就是他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.64,0:11:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是酷德·望·朱魯愛特吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.31,0:11:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.30,0:11:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.96,0:11:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.61,0:12:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雄心之中{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.21,0:12:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,懷抱大智{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.11,0:12:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,締結契約{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.43,0:12:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同契了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.12,0:12:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是說不會錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.04,0:12:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺悟吧 酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.55,0:12:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙把酷和龍搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.08,0:12:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.57,0:12:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確 我就是酷德·望·朱魯愛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.73,0:12:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍 為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.40,0:12:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道不好奇嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.24,0:12:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.22,0:12:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒印象了 做過什麼對不起你的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.09,0:12:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仇恨是沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.09,0:12:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.45,0:12:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.24,0:12:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被命令要除掉你而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.78,0:12:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂 別逃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.99,0:13:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,疼疼疼 發生什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.62,0:13:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.49,0:13:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.29,0:13:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.11,0:13:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾 我們也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.68,0:13:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自動操縱設置總該有的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.18,0:13:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.13,0:13:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是已經壞了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.09,0:13:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼啊 正在興頭上來攪和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.57,0:13:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩子就乖乖地待一邊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.19,0:13:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.74,0:13:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾 我就來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小不點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.42,0:13:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒空左顧右盼地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.60,0:13:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.40,0:14:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來你也真夠倒霉的 酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.49,0:14:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是沒得到七煌寶樹什麼的就不用受這罪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.18,0:14:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想致我於死地是為了得到七煌寶樹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.11,0:14:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常正確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.53,0:14:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要得到已經同契過的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同契者太礙事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是受了誰的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.03,0:14:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了死得瞑目?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.90,0:14:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK 就告訴你好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.87,0:14:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是ChaosChoir的特工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.91,0:14:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ChaosChoir 那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.86,0:14:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,服務結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.36,0:14:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什...什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.54,0:14:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋 居然騙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.42,0:14:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朋友的性命被盯上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.40,0:14:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少應該知道敵人的真實身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.30,0:14:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的名字是龍威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.98,0:14:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠完全保護協會守護翼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.51,0:14:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真有一套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.09,0:15:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久沒有好好打一仗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.63,0:15:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我決不放過那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.96,0:15:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要我一來 情勢就會出現大逆轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.54,0:15:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了 前輩的掩護可不是鬧著玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.77,0:15:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可是在飛天艇之上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.01,0:15:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩的攻擊使得機體破壞的話就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.13,0:15:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要掩護我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.85,0:15:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩 幸好你來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.55,0:15:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一個人實在對付不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.14,0:15:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請務必助我一臂之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.87,0:15:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.09,0:15:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了解救我可愛的後輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.93,0:15:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就全力以赴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她根本沒搞懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.56,0:15:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可可威特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.21,0:15:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小意思 包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.21,0:15:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得...得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.69,0:15:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彫蟲小技就來攻擊根本不值一提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.85,0:15:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可可威特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.71,0:16:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 要出那招了是吧 葛雷亞茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.44,0:16:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只為唯一的聽眾唱這首歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.45,0:16:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吾之台上{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.95,0:16:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心浮動不定{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.11,0:16:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吾之聲中{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.42,0:16:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死去{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吾中之我{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.60,0:16:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要什麼{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇敢地{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.00,0:16:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實地支撐{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.88,0:16:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是人類發出的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.81,0:16:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歌聲產生彈性波動攻擊煌珠的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.60,0:16:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.29,0:16:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音波之初弦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.76,0:16:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.27,0:16:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.09,0:16:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的歌聲使得這艘船都破破爛爛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.86,0:16:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀 太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.07,0:16:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再弄得破一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.98,0:16:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來一首安可曲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也不別輸給他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.35,0:16:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 在這兒使出絕招的話空賊艇會被毀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.46,0:16:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是這樣下去會被打敗的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.65,0:17:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保住飛船 同時還要打敗他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底該怎麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.88,0:17:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這得分不像是你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.37,0:17:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,庫魯斯輔佐官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點辦法都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論怎麼做都打不倒一開始的那個靶子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.02,0:17:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我把程序設置成那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.55,0:17:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是認真聰明的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.08,0:17:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想把一切做得完美的天性既是你的優點也是你的缺點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.91,0:17:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,缺點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.35,0:17:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以你的技術如果不拘泥於一開始的那個靶子的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.81,0:17:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其餘的全部都應已打倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.56,0:17:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是由於你太想要完美也就失去了所有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.57,0:18:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白我想說的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.10,0:18:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有的時候不犧牲一些東西是無法向前邁進的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.99,0:18:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.75,0:18:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一曲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.20,0:18:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很優美的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.82,0:18:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會睡得很香的哦 永遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.63,0:18:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東風之鈽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.34,0:18:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.60,0:18:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這力量...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.07,0:18:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說你就是酷德·望·朱魯愛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.13,0:18:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來一次 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.67,0:18:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.53,0:18:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.88,0:18:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再這樣下去 飛船會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.23,0:18:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掩護就交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.50,0:18:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩也住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.12,0:18:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就連你一起打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.27,0:18:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.53,0:18:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別想東想西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.14,0:18:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在只能使出所有的力量了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇雅 並唱頌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.65,0:18:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吾之性命{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.59,0:19:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要滅就滅{\a6}
