Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.13,0:19:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,末羅之斬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.27,0:19:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波濤洶涌為之徵兆{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.17,0:19:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,澄淨心靈靜聽{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.83,0:19:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祈求海神之救贖{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.80,0:19:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.62,0:19:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩篇頌詞並行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.99,0:19:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朝向大海之原{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.37,0:19:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並唱頌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.50,0:19:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敞開雙手{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鎮天之捧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.37,0:20:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.90,0:20:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣 不是要墜落了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.23,0:20:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不也發射了那麼多導彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.93,0:20:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個垂直尾翼而已 沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.69,0:20:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停...停下了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於你來說幹得很漂亮嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.72,0:20:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼亂來的決斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.60,0:20:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 或許是多虧了酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.50,0:20:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀哎呀 好不容易接近了七煌寶樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.70,0:20:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你什麼任務都沒達成嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.28,0:20:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可沒聽說守護翼的人也同行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.47,0:20:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算要與守護翼對峙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.88,0:21:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可是ChaosChoir的精銳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.09,0:21:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說的沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.98,0:21:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葛雷亞茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.30,0:21:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有什麼要說的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.35,0:21:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再給我一次機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.31,0:21:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會完成任務的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.43,0:21:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.27,0:21:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,廢棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.49,0:21:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.51,0:22:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼前的現實太令人難以置信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.08,0:22:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在此刻的幸福是真實還是假象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.29,0:23:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下回 戰慄的煌珠獵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.86,0:23:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第八唱 戰慄的煌珠獵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.38,0:23:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即便如此少女也依然想相信

